{"word":"λαλιά","slug":"λαλιά","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λαλιά</b></el> <el>(λᾰλιά, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λαλέω'><el>λαλέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>talking, talk, chat</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>speech, conversation</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b>; <i>talkativeness, loquacity</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a form of speech, dialect</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}